token_info.name: ChARon's Obols
token_info.description: Pay ChARon for your journey to the underworld.  An Augmented Reality experiment using <model-viewer> created by @fdoganis.  iOS (recommended): 3D + AR face tracking, one coin over each eye. Android: 3D + AR world tracking, a single coin that you can view in AR.  Check the compatibility with your device!
